(3, 'Front-End Web Developer', '<p><p>Breakthrough Design Group is looking for a Front-End Web Developer on a contract or part-time basis with potential for full-time hire.</p> <p>Your primary responsibilities will be development-related; converting designs and layouts for professional websites, web software applications, and other web/mobile applications as needed, producing Responsive HTML5, CSS3 & JavaScript to implement these designs.  You will also help with Search Engine Optimization upgrades, and custom WordPress theme development.</p> <p>Candidate must dream bigger than we do (and we dream big), and must live his/her life for love, character, and truth.  Candidate must love people, see the value of a problem, and must have a desire to make something bigger, better out of their short time on this earth.</p> <p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Requirements:</strong></p> <ul> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Love for responsive, minimalist HTML5, CSS3, JS code<br /></strong></li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">WordPress theme dev </strong>– Some familiarity, expert level not required<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><br /></strong></li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Currently live, demonstrable sites</strong></li> <li>Experience with Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator</li> <li>Experience in cross-browser compatibility in IE, Firefox, Safari, Chrome, Including Tablets, Phones, etc.</li> </ul> <p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Pluses:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Deeper JavaScript, jQuery development</li> <li>Design experience (not required, but welcomed)</li> <li>Focus in page load speed</li> <li>Experience w/ PHP</li> </ul> <p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Location:</strong></p> <ul> <li>Anywhere in the US, preferably near the East Coast.</li> </ul> <p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Benefits:</strong></p> <ul> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Flexible Family-First Scheduling -</strong> BDG exists to ensure the enduring health and happiness of our people, and their families.  Each team member creates their own schedule, that may evolve and adjust as life demands.</li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Work can be done remotely</strong></li> <li>Vacation, Sick & Holidays Included – After 6 months</li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Learning & Advancement Included</strong> – An ongoing budget, and a portion of every team member’s time may be devoted to their own desired learning project.</li> <li>Technology, Food, and Productivity Benefits – Provided as team member excels</li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Partnership / Commission / Bonus Pay</strong> – May be provided if person becomes a key team member.</li> <li><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Community Involvement</strong> – If desired, team member may participate in programs at BDG designed to help those in our community that need it.</li> </ul></p>', '2017-11-17 07:42:44', 1, '4', 'Breakthrough Design', 5, 'Breakthrough Design', 'http://breakthroughdesign.com/', 'Near East Coast USA', 'https://d2fcz5no062gar.cloudfront.net/assets/images/defaults/company-blank.png', 'https://breakthroughdesign.com/join/', 'https://authenticjobs.com/jobs/30032/front-end-web-developer', NULL, 1, 8);
